stakes shall be returned.</li>
<li>Change
 
    
of Venue: If a match venue is changed, bets already placed will stand
 
    
providing the home team is still designated as such. If the home and
 
    
away team for a listed match are reversed, then bets placed based on
 
    
the original listing will be void.</li></ul>
